Caravan Survival Guide (Explore Australia) - 2nd Edition (2012).epub Gooner

Publisher: Hardie Grant Books; 2nd edition edition (March 1, 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1741173833
ISBN-13: 978-1741173833

In Caravan Survival Guide, John Basham shares his detailed knowledge to help you deal with the multiple challenges of touring in your caravan. Driving skills, troubleshooting and maintenance are all covered using case studies, checklists, hints, tips and cautions. This is the book every caravanner needs before they leave home
